					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/06/30/karl-denninger-on-price-dictates-credit-illusions-and-the-healthcare-fiasco/">Karl Denninger on Price Dictates, Credit Illusions and the Healthcare&nbsp;Fiasco</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">June 30, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/06/30/karl-denninger-on-price-dictates-credit-illusions-and-the-healthcare-fiasco/#respond" title="Comment on Karl Denninger on Price Dictates, Credit Illusions and the Healthcare&nbsp;Fiasco">Leave a comment</a></span>
